 "remarks": "Spacious split level home set on one acre. Enter into the large and welcoming foyer to find large rooms throughout. Starting with an updated kitchen with quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, an abundace of cabinet space and room for a large table. Living room with fireplace and formal dining room. A half bath and laundry room complete the main level. Upper level offers four spacious bedrooms all with hardwood floors. Primary bedroom has a private bath and walk-in closet. The family bathroom serves the three additional bedrooms with double sinks. Huge lower level family room has sliders allowing easy access to the yard. Enjoy the large private yard with both patio and large deck. There is plenty of space left for the kids to play. A two car garage and generator hook up complete this home. This three road enclave offers quiet living while being conveniently located to everything Stamford has to offer.",
